{"tid":615143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔比投稿既名校Secret 仲叫唔叫Secret page?","createTime":"2018-04-03T06:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T08:20:31.000Z","uid":137840,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0bbc4e250096a3065193085c941668a31a5af5a9","tid":615143,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"[ADMIN] 有關事件跟進如下：<br />\n<br />\n1）經閱讀各方留言及投遞意見後，由於資源及人手所限，本專頁無力實行一個能滿足各方要求的帖文審批制度，故有關匿名分享機制將無限期停止。<br />\n2）已封帳號將於日內全部解除。惟解封作業需時較長，請見諒。<br />\n3）本專頁其後將會嘗試分享或創作有關校園生活及學生關心的內容。<br />\n<br />\n敬希垂注。謝謝各位。<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/141752_2a00afb277ba10f9aeca1a1a3296e719.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F141752_2a00afb277ba10f9aeca1a1a3296e719.png&h=12cd47c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔比再分享Secret 既secret page 開黎托柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n執左佢啦<br />\n係度再次感激各位巴打絲打 先有今日咁既結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696ed992633a31ab0be8f81de3206c1e442000ed","tid":615143,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4f4ec41f5d8128f182b2684a9c63b0eeff7f68","tid":615143,"uid":35001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"00後要暴動了"},{"pid":"1ae78d8c5ef1d8ac4812b81c7c61bd03bd2e7684","tid":615143,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e4f4ec41f5d8128f182b2684a9c63b0eeff7f68","tid":615143,"uid":3